{"type": "article", "id": 42298, "title": "谁说地毯一定只能是规则形状？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-22T23:04:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34187, "name": "Futura"}, {"id": 41717, "name": "ODDO Architects"}, {"id": 41718, "name": "Lim + Lu"}, {"id": 41719, "name": "Maze"}, {"id": 41720, "name": "太平地毯"}, {"id": 41721, "name": "Genis Carreras"}, {"id": 41722, "name": "Louise Hederström"}, {"id": 41723, "name": "Brett Foxwell"}, {"id": 41724, "name": "bedtimes"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 126, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170623070411xqbJSyZFVfksEYnz.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Philographics by Genis Carreras</h3><p>要理解抽象的哲学概念不一定非得通过难懂的文字。四年前，西班牙设计师 Genis Carreras 在 Kickstarter 上推出了一个名为 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/geniscarreras/philographics-big-ideas-in-simple-shapes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Philographics</a> 的项目，以简洁的几何图形和色彩诠释了 95 个深奥的哲学理论。项目的成功为 Carreras 吸引到了出版商，目前已经发行了五种语言的书籍。最近，作为 Kickstarter Gold 计划的一部分，这个备受欢迎的创意开启了新一轮众筹，在书籍的基础上推出了一本 24 页的明信片书。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/geniscarreras/kickstarter-gold-philographics\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与，售价从 10 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017062221383693KoLGewf4pINHrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213836DFWZfj71NkiqYmRI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.579412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213837j76lASVaCmsDWwzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.920588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213836GIQhOyDXdaLSRgHN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213837koCSfzN4gPh6dy3L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hanger by Louise Hederström</h3><p>瑞典设计师 <a href=\"http://www.louisehederstrom.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louise Hederström</a> 以家乡大片的森林为灵感，为设计公司 <a href=\"https://www.mazeinterior.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maze</a> 打造了四款极简风格的衣架。经过弯曲的涂漆金属管分别构成了整棵树、树冠或是树枝的轮廓，空置的情况下也可以作为墙面装饰品使用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.mazeinterior.se/en/4-hangers-racks-storage-design\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些衣架，售价从 345 瑞典克朗起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706222138525YtzuNcWTkDORI6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213852yQABpHMtvoxaDJ82.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213853MtaPbR5V9FY3yvdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Birdwalk by ODDO Architects</h3><p>为了让观鸟爱好者可以更方便地欣赏到鸟儿们的全貌，双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/oddoarchitects\" rel=\"nofollow\">ODDO Architects</a> 借鉴了秀场的 T 台设计，打造了一个可以让小鸟们“走秀”的鸟屋。金字塔形的小屋内设有一个饲料槽，一侧的木墙上还配备了一扇圆形的小窗户，供“模特”们一窥自己的“仰慕者”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706222139077p32TfrZ8jcbisIJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.378973\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213907waNeoHxsGCnbqJiD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213908kXQ6U9ma1JiAWbpq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213907pboZlyHmR9fxnO0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.125917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reform by Lim + Lu</h3><p>在纽约国际当代家具展（<a href=\"http://www.icff.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ICFF</a>）上，香港跨领域设计公司林子设计（<a href=\"http://www.icff.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lim + Lu</a>）带来了他们为地毯制造商太平地毯（<a href=\"https://houseoftaiping.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tai Ping</a>）设计的模块化地毯系列 Reform。这些地毯由彩色圆圈构成，可以根据需要组合出不同的形状。由 100% 羊毛制成的 Refrom II 采用的是明亮生动的配色，而材质更加多元的 Refrom I 走的是让人联想到大理石和金属的混搭路线。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622214038L3jAXlodZt0e2TOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622214037dKSAuFm2sNOLWXQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622214038z4onumE5bZO8WptM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pizza Affair by Futura</h3><p>还记得那个黑白色的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33599.html\">街头涂鸦风披萨盒</a>吗？它背后的设计团队 <a href=\"http://byfutura.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Futura</a> 最近带来了一个令人意想不到的食品包装。当团队收到委托，为名为 The Pizza Affair 的法国餐厅操刀品牌形象时，他们大胆地将 70 年代的软色情画面和色彩鲜艳的抽象图形结合在一起，巧妙地勾起人们的食欲。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213930x7pe1nt3YGcCaqOd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213929zbPmcSQI5y480WAg.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706222139290e5RFkcyu1AjS2Yp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213929bnruF6UafNSJGHQ7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213930BbWwcgCs1Spame7X.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213930r7v0dNshuZOjL6cp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>WoodSwimmer by Brett Foxwell &amp; bedtimes</h3><p>当一块木头被锯断时，你有没有好奇过它们的内部结构究竟发生了怎样的变化？以定格和延时动画见长的艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.bfophoto.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brett Foxwell</a> 与音乐人 <a href=\"http://bedtimes.xxx/music\" rel=\"nofollow\">bedtimes</a> 联手推出了一段名为 WoodSwimmer 的 MV，记录下了锯木过程中木头横截面发生的变化。在这段流畅的视频中，木纹仿佛化作一片棕色的水域，让人大开眼界。你可以通过<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/196683500\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>欣赏到完整视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170622213948pRKOYyiqbhTLnxz0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490625\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706222139501RjLlWTan5euhCzk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}